    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small cylindrical pleats arranged in a row, thus resembling a military cartridge belt, used decoratively to give a military effect to costume and hangings.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
